Xfburn is a GTK+ 2 GUI frontend for Libisoburn.
This is useful for creating CDs and DVDs from files
on your computer or ISO images downloaded from elsewhere. 

Xfburn, est une application GTK+ 2 pour la gravure de CDs/DVDs/BDs
ainsi que d'images ISO.

